Calladmin plugin for BigBrotherBot (www.bigbrotherbot.net)
=============================================================

By Mr.Click


Description
-----------
This plugin send an admin request over a Teamspeak 3 server or a Mumble (murmur) server.
In order to work properly you need to include in your b3 configuration at least one of the following plugins:

  - Teamspeak 3 Plugin (courgette) : http://forum.bigbrotherbot.net/downloads/?sa=view;down=144
  - Mumble Plugin (BlackMamba) : http://forum.bigbrotherbot.net/downloads/?sa=view;down=111
  
If both plugins are missing your b3 will fail to start

Installation
------------

 * copy calladmin.py into b3/extplugins
 * copy calladmin.xml into b3/extplugins/conf
 
<plugin name="calladmin" config="@b3/extplugins/conf/calladmin.xml"/>

Remember to include this plugin after the Teamspeak 3 Plugin and/or the Mumble Plugin or your b3 fail to start

